title: Clay and Buck’s Countdown to Election Day Episode 3 - Oct 9 2022
itunes:title: Clay and Buck’s Countdown to Election Day Episode 3 - Oct 9 2022
description:
Four great candidates from across the country – Tudor Dixon (MI), Tiffany Smiley (WA), Sen. Mike Lee (UT), and Rep. Ted Budd (NC) -- plus the three Senate races that will decide who wins control.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
